    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <note type="editorial" resp="#ww" place="top">Sent to Rolleston, Ireland, Sept. 20
                '84.</note>

            <p>Write now to acknowledge yours from Ireland just rec'd.&#8212;to send you
                congratulations on return home with wife and children&#8212;and prayers for good
                future to you all&#8212;will write in time, what I have to say about the new phase
                of the trans[lation] enterprise.<ptr target="loc.05825_n1"/> I am about as usual in
                health&#8212;one point worse&#8212;thre[atened] with total and permanent loss of
                walking power&#8212; </p>

            
        </body>   
